Class SimDimerMEAMGB

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.simulation.Simulation
      • etomica.dimer.SimDimerMEAMGB
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISimulation

    public class SimDimerMEAMGB
extends Simulation
    Simulation using Henkelman's Dimer method to find a saddle point for an adatom of Sn on a surface, modeled with MEAM.
